# 📖 Talking Dictionary

[![GitHub Pages](https://img.shields.io/badge/Live-Demo-brightgreen)](https://animesh-mathur23.github.io/Talking-Dictionary/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue)](LICENSE)

A web-based dictionary application that provides definitions, pronunciations, and usage examples with audio playback.

![Talking Dictionary Screenshot](/assets/images/screenshot.png) *(Replace with actual screenshot)*

## ✨ Features

- 🔍 **Word Definitions** - Comprehensive word meanings
- 🔊 **Audio Pronunciations** - Hear correct word pronunciation
- 📚 **Examples & Usage** - Contextual sentence examples
- 🏷️ **Part of Speech** - Clear grammatical categorization
- 📱 **Responsive Design** - Works on all devices
- ⚡ **Instant Results** - Fast API response with async loading

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

**Frontend:**
- HTML5
- CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid)
- Vanilla JavaScript (ES6+)

**API Integration:**
- [Free Dictionary API](https://dictionaryapi.dev/)

**Tools & Services:**
- GitHub Pages (Hosting)
- Visual Studio Code (Development)
- Chrome DevTools (Debugging)

